#

Shrimp Fried Rice

25 min
$12.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

shellfishegg

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinnut-free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main

Tags:

easyquicksatisfying

Description

A savory combination of fresh shrimp, colorful vegetables, and perfectly cooked rice, all stir-fried to perfection!

Ingredients

  • shrimp, peeled and deveined: 1 cup
  • cooked rice: 2 cups
  • peas and carrots (frozen): 1 cup
  • eggs: 2
  • green onions, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • ginger, minced: 1 teaspoon
